Note: at 3ct, GIA D-VVS1 ($5,962) is actually priced below IGI D-VVS1 ($6,215) — the GIA premium reverses at this quality tier, reflecting market supply dynamics rather than certification hierarchy alone. Always compare actual listed prices, not certification assumptions.

