## 4ct Lab Grown Cushion Cut Diamond

The 4ct lab grown cushion has no practical equivalent in the natural market for most buyers. The lowest-priced natural 4ct cushion on Blue Nile is $85,685. Lab 4ct D-VVS1 starts at $7,096.

