The 4ct tier illustrates the full scale of The Certification Gap in reverse: GIA 4ct D-VVS1 at $7,412 matches IGI 4ct D-VVS1 exactly. At this carat weight, GIA and IGI have converged at the VVS1 tier. The D-IF tier shows the familiar split: IGI D-IF at $17,598 versus natural equivalent above $85,000.

